    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_9bbe1b58"><bpmn:text>Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 1 lit. a&#10;Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 1 lit. b&#10;Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 1 lit. c&#10;Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 1 lit. d&#10;Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 1 lit. e&#10;Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 1 lit. f&#10;Check exception in Art. 49 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 49 Abs. 1&#10;Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND LimitedTo AND Legitimate Interest</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_9fad4c58"><bpmn:text>Notify the competent supervisory authority&#10;No exception under Art. 49 Abs. 1&#10;Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND LimitedTo AND Legitimate Interest</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_23fa84fe"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 49 Abs. 3&#10;Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND Original Consent Given AND Data Subject Gave Consent</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_1d492bf2"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 49 Abs. 3&#10;Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND Transfer to Third Country</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_a281da2e"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 49 Abs. 3&#10;Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND Legitimate Interest AND Transfer to Third Country</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_aaf44ae9"><bpmn:text>Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND Recognize AND Transfer to Third Country</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_3fe02688"><bpmn:text>Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND LegalClaim AND Transfer to Third Country</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_6b0bdf79"><bpmn:text>Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND Original Consent Given AND Data Subject Gave Consent</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_75256181"><bpmn:text>Applies when: Transfer to International Organization AND Implement Measure AND Maintain Processing Record AND Inform the Public</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_2afac4be"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 49 Abs. 1&#10;Applies when: Maintain Processing Record AND Transfer to Third Country AND Implement Measure AND Legitimate Interest</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
